{"tid":46837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄駐土耳其大使遭槍殺　槍手為休班警員","createTime":"2016-12-20T02:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T05:49:45.000Z","uid":37856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e64f39e621dcd24ec3a48e18ce0ff5798a3f2f8","tid":46837,"uid":37856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/798760/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F798760%2F&d=hxoshttU99KpEZZndaxDNqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=0a7f3174\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F798760%2F&h=12a673a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/798760/</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯駐土耳其大使卡爾洛夫，在土耳其首都安卡拉出席活動時遭到槍擊死亡，美國政府迅速表態，對事件加以譴責。敘利亞政府也指責這是「卑鄙的罪行」。<br />\n<br />\n卡爾洛夫（Andrey Karlov）周一於安卡拉出席「土耳其人眼中的俄羅斯」展覽開幕禮，一名身穿黑色西裝的槍手一直站在身後，他突然以阿拉伯語高呼「真主偉大」，掏出一把手槍向卡爾洛夫連開多槍。事發時有大批記者在場，直擊整個過程，當時槍手又用槍指向在場其他人士，並高喊「毋忘阿勒頗」，他其後擊毀場內多張相片，遭當場擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其安全部門指，槍手22歲，是安卡拉休班警務人員。俄羅斯則指事件為恐怖襲擊，是俄羅斯外交史上災難的一天。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人柯比（John Kirby）指：「我們譴責此暴行，無論是何方所為。我們支持卡爾洛夫大使和他的家人，也為他們祈禱。」<br />\n<br />\n敘利亞外交部發表聲明指，以最強烈的言詞譴責這個懦弱的恐怖主義襲擊行動。又指這卑鄙的罪行再次證實有迫切需要打擊恐怖主義。"},{"pid":"8f90bb03d383c022f0786b08b3f69c9e7ddc9d51","tid":46837,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:49:38.000Z","msg":"全世界既休班警都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放左工就會作奸犯科"},{"pid":"50de03e2e20cfda01fa7e7e69eb72a5fab54c036","tid":46837,"uid":33837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:50:46.000Z","msg":"諗起斐特南大公"},{"pid":"4a481c0c95eb153435f8ac5bdb50de4b6b202606","tid":46837,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起斐特南大公</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame 莫非期待已久既世界大戰續漸行近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf92ade25d6f4ea925f649e601e62fc63e5dfaf","tid":46837,"uid":33837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗起斐特南大公</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame 莫非期待已久既世界大戰續漸行近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要好多人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9cb471403fdd201430dfa797fd2434e525b09c","tid":46837,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"俄佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e8a1672f95b03164831094d0640747e438c533","tid":46837,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:57:55.000Z","msg":"休班警得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f40ee4fceb5eb1a3f9d85035783ca2154ee07eb","tid":46837,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"全球最大犯罪集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d416a08ce50b387ebef77ea7b1511944b9e4f9","tid":46837,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}